<br>
I am a firm believer that this system is much better in a guild system because it encourages teamwork and guild values instead of merely relying on randomness which in my opinion just encourages greed.  It does depend on people however every officer in Vision tries to be as fair as possible some to the extent of passing on loot they want just because they would feel bad taking the item.  <br>
<br>
SOME of the Officers / Class Leaders have had to be FORCED to take loot when they originally declined thinking others would benefit more.  That kinda attitude is truely what Vision is all about helping each other to get better and having fun at the same time.<br>
